aibrain

Class Deal

  • java.lang.Object
    • aibrain.Deal

  • public class Deal
extends java.lang.Object
    Basic DTO for deals. Offers represent the set of actions that each player is offering to do (in addition to any other actions they might do outside of the deal) should the deal be accepted. Threats are not currently implemented, but will represent what each player will do unilaterally if the deal is "broken". Not all players in the game need to have entries in the deal, but any player who does appear must have an offer and a threat, and all plans must be of the same length.
